<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”罗西在巧克力酱里挣扎。它又黏又重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西慢慢站起来，然后转圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转得越来越快，就像龙卷风一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巧克力酱被甩了出去，溅得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就变干净了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 勒·斯威特去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西从一扇窗户飞了出去。“他在那儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特开着一辆送货车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车子飞快地开向城里。另外一辆送货车翻倒在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞向第二辆送货车。司机站在车旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机举起两手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“勒·斯威特把我挤到路边！他抢走了我的送货区。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说我再也不能送全麦饼干了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在开始，人们都只吃勒·斯威特的甜甜圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人疯了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的下一个送货区是哪里？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城小学。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得马上去那儿，要快！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西一只手抓着司机，另一只抓着送货车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西飞向天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机笑了。“哇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当罗西飞过美罗城的时候，她往下看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了演《大力士》的演员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在跟一个人自拍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西想，“他现在看起来很正常。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们不会一直保持僵尸状态的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们正在食堂吃午饭的时候，一个男人走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他手里拿着一摞盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫皮特·勒·斯威特。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来给大家送免费甜甜圈了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都拍手，欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特举起一个甜甜圈。“谁想要第一个？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我！”杰克跑过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特递给他一个甜甜圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，食堂的门猛地被打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别吃那个！”罗西大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克吓得跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>甜甜圈从他手里飞了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它划过空中，刚好掉在勒·斯威特的嘴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探冲了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“您可以把这个僵尸送进监狱了，侦探先生！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机走了进来。“谁想吃饼干？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你错过了火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉在休息时间对罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，真可惜。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔怀疑地看了罗西一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总是错过火箭女孩儿。我想知道为什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”罗西不知道该怎么说 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还错过了别的事情！”杰克突然说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个奇怪的人吃了甜甜圈以后变成了僵尸！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，特勒尔还是一幅很怀疑的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>